"Advance Wars"  is a turn-based tactics video game developed for the Game Boy Advance by Intelligent Systems and published by Nintendo. Advance Wars is the first game in the Advance Wars series of video games, followed by "Advance Wars 2: Black Hole Rising" (also for the Game Boy Advance).
